<h2 class="p-name post__title"><a href="/blog/2023/opml-rss-categories/">OPML and RSS feeds for categories</a></h2>
<p class="post__byline">
By
<span class="p-author h-card">
<span class="p-name">Phil Gyford</span>
on
<time class="dt-published" datetime="2023-01-15 10:54:00">2023-01-15</time>
</p>
<div class="e-summary">
<p>If there are specific topics you're interested in, this is a good update for you. You can now download&nbsp;<a href="http://opml.org" title="About OPML">OPML</a> files of all the blogs currently in each category, and&nbsp;follow RSS feeds of the blogs added to individual categories.</p>
</div>
